  <ExtendedSection language="en">
    <Title><![CDATA[Various ways to change the contents behavior]]></Title>
    <Section>
      <Caption><![CDATA[Widget configuration]]></Caption>
      <Text name="Text0">
        <links/>
        <content><![CDATA[<p>Each value has a comfortable way to specify it. Say "true" by clicking a checkbox, refer to an image by chosing it from a gallery and so on. Widgets provide various ways to enter a value. Check out which widgets are available, how to configure them for your content type and how to write your own widgets.</p>]]></content>
      </Text>
